<i>adverb</i>: 얼큰히 [얼큰히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>얼큰히 [얼큰히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spicily; hotly</dd><br>
<dd>입 안이 얼얼할 정도로 약간 맵게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being a bit spicy enough to feel tingly in one's mouth.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tipsily; drunkenly</dd><br>
<dd>술에 취하여 정신이 약간 흐릿하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of one's mind being a bit foggy because one is drunk.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>